dct_title_s: Península de Baja California : mapa turístico de carreteras 2010 = Peninsula Baja California : road & recreation map 2010 / $c Producción Carlos Esparza Ramón. (Recto)
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by spot heights. Title on verso: Baja California : road and recreation map, 7a edición. On recto: Baja California norte. On verso: Baja California sur. Map continued on verso. Map shows time zones, 7classes of roads, railroads, and tourist sites. Includes 15 ancillary maps.
